---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn more about CyberClub and our mission">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-forest-green">About Sacramento State CyberClub</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Sacramento State CyberClub is a student-run organization at California State University, Sacramento
          dedicated to fostering a community of cybersecurity enthusiasts, from curious beginners to experienced hackers.
          We believe that cybersecurity skills are essential in today's digital world, and we're committed
          to making them accessible to all Hornet students.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-pale-gold border-l-4 border-light-gold p-6 my-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-forest-green mb-2">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            To empower students with practical cybersecurity skills through hands-on learning,
            ethical hacking challenges, and collaborative knowledge sharing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-forest-green mt-12 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest-green mb-2">üèÜ CTF Competitions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Regular participation in Capture The Flag competitions, both internal and external.
              Test your skills in cryptography, web exploitation, reverse engineering, and more.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest-green mb-2">üìö Workshops</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Weekly workshops covering topics from beginner-friendly introductions to advanced
              exploitation techniques and security research.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest-green mb-2">ü§ù Community</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Join a supportive community where members share knowledge, collaborate on challenges,
              and help each other grow as security professionals.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-forest-green mb-2">üíº Career Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Network with industry professionals, attend guest lectures, and develop skills
              that employers value in the cybersecurity field.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-forest-green mt-12 mb-4">Our Focus Areas</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
          <li><strong class="text-forest-green">Web Application Security:</strong> XSS, SQLi, CSRF, and modern web vulnerabilities</li>
          <li><strong class="text-forest-green">Binary Exploitation:</strong> Buffer overflows, ROP, heap exploitation</li>
          <li><strong class="text-forest-green">Cryptography:</strong> Classic and modern crypto challenges</li>
          <li><strong class="text-forest-green">Reverse Engineering:</strong> Binary analysis and malware research</li>
          <li><strong class="text-forest-green">Network Security:</strong> Traffic analysis, network protocols, and attacks</li>
          <li><strong class="text-forest-green">Digital Forensics:</strong> Incident response and evidence analysis</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-forest-green mt-12 mb-4">Meeting Schedule</h2>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-forest-green">Regular Meetings:</strong> Every Monday, 7:00 PM - 9:00 PM
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            <strong class="text-forest-green">Location:</strong> Room 245, Engineering Building
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong class="text-forest-green">Online:</strong> Join us on Discord for virtual meetings and 24/7 discussions
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block bg-forest-green text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-dark-forest transition-colors"
          >
            Join Us Today
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
